<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta content="IE=edge" http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible">
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport">
    <title>{{ title }}</title>

    <style>
      *,
      *::after,
      *::before {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html {
        font-family: sans-serif;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        background-color: #1F2937;
        color: #F9FAFB;
      }

      main {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 1024px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 20px;
      }

      h1 {
        text-align: center;
      }

      pre {
        overflow-x: auto;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 16px;
        background-color: #374151;
      }

      a {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #7DD3FC;
      }

      a:hover {
        color: #BAE6FD;
      }

      a:focus-visible {
        color: #BAE6FD;
        outline: 3px solid #BAE6FD;
        outline-offset: 2px;
      }

      ul li {
        margin-bottom: 0.3em;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <h1>Selim's personal repository for debian-based distros</h1>
      <p>
                This repository contains packages of the open source software that 
                                                                                                                                            I frequently use, mostly automatically pulled directly from the
                                                                                                                                            github release pages and crudely packed with dpkg-deb.
                                                                                                                                            Tested on Ubuntu 20.04 and nothing more.
            </p>

      <p>To use this repository, populate your apt sources list and import the GPG key:</p>
      <pre>echo "deb http://deb.selim13.ru/repo/ sid main" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/deb-selim13-ru.list
wget -qO - http://deb.selim13.ru/repo.gpg.key | sudo apt-key add -</pre>

      <ul>
        {% for package in packages %}
          <li>
            {% if package.homepage %}
              <a href="{{ package.homepage }}">{{ package.name }}</a>
            {% else %}
              {{ package.name }}
            {% endif %}

            {{ package.version }}

            {% if package.description %}
                            &mdash;
                            {{ package.description }}
            {% endif %}

                        [{{ package.archs | join(" ") }}]
                    </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>

      <p>
        <a href="http://deb.selim13.ru/repo/">Repository directory listing</a><br>
        <a href="https://github.com/selim13/linux-packages/">
          Scripts for updating packages and this page
        </a>
      </p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
